Individual Project

Help text for CLI:

Mutually modes:
-s	 	   scrape mode
-f   	 	   fetch mode, can be used with analyse
-a   	       	   analyse mode, can be used with fetch

--help	     	   this help text
--version	   show version

--depth_limit	   how far back to fetch/analyse article history
--titles	   page titles. multiple titles can be specified,
		   split with the '|' character, ie:
		   --titles "philosophy|music"
--scrape_limit	   
